			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Use Monitoring to Support Future Action">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
				<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="As you implement actions, you can monitor how hazards, equity, and resilient systems are changing after your community has gone through the ERB process.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
				<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="The benefits of monitoring ERB planning outcomes include:">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Checking that actions align with stated priorities">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Evaluate outcomes of resilience actions">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Increase transparency of the implementation process">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Maintain shared understanding of equitable resilience">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Gauge how the relationships you've built are going">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Increase support for future actions">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
				<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
