			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Work with your core team and other local experts to figure out how to carry out monitoring to evaluate outcomes and support implementation efforts. Identify a team member or local group as the 'Monitoring Lead' of each action. You may use the Monitoring Plan as a guide.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
